ury!<br></li><li> Accompany Hercules on the first extraterrestrial labour!<br></li><li> Show off your stylish space suit!<br></li><li> Grow stronger with alien booster pills!<br></li><li> Blow up an asteroid full of cheese!<br></li><li> Travel with Cerberus to infinity and bow-wow!</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1026070/extras/d4ee53fbf67485f59be00aafea279882.avif?t=1587986742\" width=614 height=161 /></span></h2>",
